dct_title_s: Intourist map of the Soviet Union and Europe showing principal transportation connections
dct_description_sm: C. S. Hammond & Co. North Decimal Degree 69.051111. South Decimal Degree 37.368056. East Decimal Degree 61.366111. West Decimal Degree -37.380833. Alternate title: Map of the Soviet Union with travel rates and suggested itineraries. Inset map: To the Far East via the Trans-Siberian railroad. Map show rairoads, airqays and steamship lines. Verso: Intourist suggested itineraries for 1936.
